Problem statement
Given the number 'n', write a code to print numbers from 1 to n in increasing order recursively.

Detailed explanation ( Input/output format, Notes, Images )
Constraints :
1 <= n <= 10000
Sample Input 1 :
 6
Sample Output 1 :
1 2 3 4 5 6
Sample Input 2 :
 4
Sample Output 2 :
1 2 3 4

//code
#include <iostream>

void print(int n) {
    if (n == 1) {
        std::cout << n << " ";
        return;
    }
    print(n - 1);
    std::cout << n << " ";
}

